---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="3 Slides"
  description="The Botsters — 3 Slides. Customer. Problem. Solution."
>
  <div class="pitch-page">

    <!-- SLIDE 01: Customer -->
    <section class="slide slide-customer">
      <div class="slide-inner">
        <div class="slide-number">01</div>
        <div class="slide-label">Customer</div>
        <h2>Anyone Who Wants Agents</h2>

        <div class="customer-grid">
          <div class="customer-card">
            <div class="customer-icon">&#127970;</div>
            <h3>Enterprise Teams</h3>
            <p>Companies deploying AI agents across internal tooling, customer support, and data pipelines — who cannot afford a breach.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="customer-card">
            <div class="customer-icon">&#128640;</div>
            <h3>Startups Building on Agents</h3>
            <p>Developers building agent-powered products who need a secure, auditable runtime — without building the infrastructure themselves.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="customer-card">
            <div class="customer-icon">&#128101;</div>
            <h3>OpenClaw Users Today</h3>
            <p>The existing community of 30,000+ OpenClaw users who are already running agents — and already exposed to the risk they don't know about yet.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="customer-card customer-card-wide">
            <div class="customer-icon">&#127757;</div>
            <h3>Anyone Who Wants Agents</h3>
            <p>The AI agent market is still at the "early adopter" stage. <strong>The bottleneck is trust, not capability.</strong> Once agents are safe enough for a non-technical user to run, the market is everyone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="slide-divider"></div>

    <!-- SLIDE 02: Problem -->
    <section class="slide slide-problem">
      <div class="slide-inner">
        <div class="slide-number">02</div>
        <div class="slide-label">Problem</div>
        <h2>OpenClaw is Insecure.<br/>Very Insecure.</h2>

        <div class="evidence-block">
          <div class="evidence-item evidence-audit">
            <div class="evidence-icon">&#128269;</div>
            <div class="evidence-body">
              <div class="evidence-source">ClawSecure Large-Scale Security Audit</div>
              <div class="evidence-date">February 16, 2026</div>
              <div class="stat-grid">
                <div class="stat">
                  <div class="stat-num">41.7%</div>
                  <div class="stat-label">of skills contained vulnerabilities<br/><span class="stat-note">~1,205+ skills</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat stat-danger">
                  <div class="stat-num">30.6%</div>
                  <div class="stat-label">High or Critical severity</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat stat-warning">
                  <div class="stat-num">22.9%</div>
                  <div class="stat-label">"Sleeper Agent" risk</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="evidence-item evidence-quote">
            <div class="evidence-icon">&#128172;</div>
            <div class="evidence-body">
              <blockquote>
                "like I was defusing a bomb"
              </blockquote>
              <div class="quote-attribution">
                <strong>Summer Yue</strong>, Director of Alignment, Meta AI Security &amp; Safety
              </div>
              <div class="quote-detail">
                &mdash; on having to physically run to her Mac mini to shut down her OpenClaw agent
              </div>
              <div class="quote-context">
                The broader concern &mdash; that AI agents have root access to everything &mdash; has been echoed widely across the community.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="slide-divider"></div>

    <!-- SLIDE 03: Solution — BSA Diagram -->
    <section class="slide slide-solution">
      <div class="slide-inner">
        <div class="slide-number">03</div>
        <div class="slide-label">Solution</div>
        <h2>Brain &middot; Spine &middot; Actuator</h2>

        <div class="bsa-diagram">

          <!-- Brain -->
          <div class="bsa-node bsa-brain">
            <div class="bsa-node-icon">&#129504;</div>
            <div class="bsa-node-name">Brain</div>
            <div class="bsa-node-sub">The AI Agent</div>
            <ul class="bsa-node-facts">
              <li>Runs inference (Claude, GPT, etc.)</li>
              <li>Never holds credentials</li>
              <li>Can't act without Spine permission</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Arrow Brain → Spine -->
          <div class="bsa-arrow">
            <div class="bsa-arrow-line"></div>
            <div class="bsa-arrow-labels">
              <span class="bsa-arrow-label">secret name only &rarr;</span>
              <span class="bsa-arrow-label">&larr; proxied response</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bsa-arrow-head">&#9660;</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Spine -->
          <div class="bsa-node bsa-spine">
            <div class="bsa-node-icon">&#128272;</div>
            <div class="bsa-node-name">Spine</div>
            <div class="bsa-node-sub">Customer-Controlled Security Layer</div>
            <ul class="bsa-node-facts">
              <li>Holds all secrets &amp; credentials</li>
              <li>Logs every inference call</li>
              <li>Grants or revokes agent access</li>
              <li>Attestation &amp; audit trail</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Arrow Spine → Actuator -->
          <div class="bsa-arrow">
            <div class="bsa-arrow-line"></div>
            <div class="bsa-arrow-labels">
              <span class="bsa-arrow-label">approved action &rarr;</span>
              <span class="bsa-arrow-label">&larr; result log</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bsa-arrow-head">&#9660;</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Actuator -->
          <div class="bsa-node bsa-actuator">
            <div class="bsa-node-icon">&#9881;&#65039;</div>
            <div class="bsa-node-name">Actuator</div>
            <div class="bsa-node-sub">The Executor</div>
            <ul class="bsa-node-facts">
              <li>Runs shell, git, browser, APIs</li>
              <li>Scoped capabilities only</li>
              <li>All actions logged before execution</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="bsa-insight">
          <strong>The Key Insight:</strong> Secrets never touch the Brain. The Brain can't act without the Spine. The Actuator can only do what the Spine permits. Security is architectural &mdash; not instructional.
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .pitch-page {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .slide {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .slide-inner {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .slide-divider {
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,107,53,0.4) 20%, rgba(255,107,53,0.4) 80%, transparent);
    margin: 0 2rem;
  }

  .slide-number {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(255,107,53,0.15);
    margin-bottom: -1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .slide-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .slide h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-text) 60%, var(--color-accent));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  /* ───── SLIDE 01: Customer ───── */
  .slide-customer {
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 40%, rgba(255,107,53,0.06) 0%, transparent 65%);
  }

  .customer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .customer-card {
    padding: 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .customer-card:hover { border-color: rgba(255,107,53,0.35); }

  .customer-card-wide {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    background: rgba(255,107,53,0.05);
    border-color: rgba(255,107,53,0.25);
  }

  .customer-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .customer-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-amber);
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }

  .customer-card-wide h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .customer-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ───── SLIDE 02: Problem ───── */
  .slide-problem {
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 30%, rgba(220,38,38,0.05) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .evidence-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .evidence-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
  }

  .evidence-audit {
    background: rgba(220,38,38,0.04);
    border-color: rgba(220,38,38,0.2);
  }

  .evidence-quote {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }

  .evidence-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  .evidence-body { flex: 1; }

  .evidence-source {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .evidence-date {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .stat {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--color-bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .stat-danger { border-color: rgba(220,38,38,0.4); background: rgba(220,38,38,0.08); }
  .stat-warning { border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.4); background: rgba(245,158,11,0.07); }

  .stat-num {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .stat-danger .stat-num { color: #ef4444; }
  .stat-warning .stat-num { color: var(--color-amber); }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .stat-note {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .quote-attribution {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .quote-detail {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .quote-context {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim, rgba(255,255,255,0.35));
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ───── SLIDE 03: Solution / BSA Diagram ───── */
  .slide-solution {
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 60%, rgba(255,107,53,0.06) 0%, transparent 65%);
  }

  .bsa-diagram {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .bsa-node {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 540px;
    padding: 2rem 2.25rem;
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border-muted);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    position: relative;
  }

  .bsa-brain {
    border-color: rgba(192,132,252,0.4);
    background: rgba(192,132,252,0.05);
  }

  .bsa-spine {
    border-color: rgba(255,107,53,0.45);
    background: rgba(255,107,53,0.06);
  }

  .bsa-actuator {
    border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.4);
    background: rgba(34,197,94,0.05);
  }

  .bsa-node-icon {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .bsa-node-name {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .bsa-brain .bsa-node-name   { color: #c084fc; }
  .bsa-spine .bsa-node-name   { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .bsa-actuator .bsa-node-name { color: #4ade80; }

  .bsa-node-sub {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .bsa-node-facts {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .bsa-node-facts li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .bsa-node-facts li::before {
    content: '›';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Arrows between nodes */
  .bsa-arrow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 540px;
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
  }

  .bsa-arrow-line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 52px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,107,53,0.25), rgba(255,107,53,0.6));
  }

  .bsa-arrow-head {
    color: rgba(255,107,53,0.6);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: -5px;
  }

  .bsa-arrow-labels {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .bsa-arrow-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-dim, rgba(255,255,255,0.28));
    white-space: nowrap;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  /* Bottom callout */
  .bsa-insight {
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(255,107,53,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,53,0.25);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .bsa-insight strong { color: var(--color-accent); }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .slide { padding: 4rem 1.25rem; }
    .customer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .customer-card-wide { grid-column: 1; }
    .stat-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .evidence-item { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    .bsa-arrow-labels { display: none; }
    .bsa-node { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
